  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/1b0511873f51c491ae5cfba563e24645.poster.avif?t=1722547872\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/1b0511873f51c491ae5cfba563e24645.webm?t=1722547872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/1b0511873f51c491ae5cfba563e24645.mp4?t=1722547872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Adapt to your new cybernetic body, combining magical and technological abilities. Face endless temporal challenges and master your powers in a simulation to defeat relentless demonic pursuers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/f3526d863ae161937579d799dad703e8.poster.avif?t=1722547872\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/f3526d863ae161937579d799dad703e8.webm?t=1722547872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/f3526d863ae161937579d799dad703e8.mp4?t=1722547872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game currently features 8 different types of weapons, 5 accessories, 6 drones, 25 passive skills, and 19 active skills to unlock in a large skill tree. There are 13 enemy variants, 4 elites, and two fully operational level bosses. The first two levels are fully playable, although my goal is to have at least 5 in the future.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072780/extras/99c47a786482bd40bec792340eb20163.avif?t=1722547872\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
